title: [Feywrot Mire, Banyan Cirque]
description: Continuations of the dwarf cypress grove to the north stretch along the cracked mud pathways.  Two large trees grow beside a small painted structure, with cotton clotheslines strung taut between their branches.  Two pair of overalls, an oversized red-checkered frock, and some frilly undergarments flap in the moonlight, as if dancing to silent music with every passing breeze.
